    <p>Cottard was <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="a queer bird"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(一个古怪的人)</code></b>. For a long while their relations went no farther than wishing each other good-day when they met on the stairs.</p>
