    <p><b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="Two crisscross strokes"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________([用手术刀]划下两条十字线后)</code></b>, and the ganglion <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="\ (ˌ)dis-ˈgȯrj \ to discharge or let go of rapidly or forcefully"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">disgorged</code></b> a mixture of blood and <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="\ ˈpəs \ 脓"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">pus</code></b>. Their limbs stretched out as far as they could manage, the sick men went on bleeding.</p>
